---
alwaysApply: true
---
Please use pnpm for all commands. That includes pnpm add, pnpm run, pnpm dev, pnpm build, pnpm exec, pnpm dlx, etc.
The main tech stack is Next.js (App Router) + React + Shadcn + Tailwind + Three.js (TSL/WebGPU).
Try to use '-primary' and dont attempt to add your own background colors.
Try to make the main part of the component default font size to keep the design consistent.
